{"version":1,"entries":{"person_4873902_translations":{"at":1774698737309,"data":{"id":4873902,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"\"Oom\" Panchaya Suwannagood is an artist from Ubon Ratchathani under Channel 7. She studies at Kasetsart University. Oom got her start in the industry as a model.","name":"Oom Panchaya Suwannagood","primary":true}}]}},"person_4746154_translations":{"at":1774698744310,"data":{"id":4746154,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Karan Abrol","primary":true}}]}},"person_1358833_translations":{"at":1774698744660,"data":{"id":1358833,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"尹治，生于五代梨园世家。 在拍完《霸王别姬》后，尹治陆续拍摄了一些电影和电视剧，后来报考了中国戏曲学院导演系。他在央视播出的电视剧《荀慧生》中扮演了梅兰芳，并得到观众的认可。此外，他在李少红导演的《雷雨》中，曾饰演过京剧名角小白春。","name":"尹治","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yin Zhi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"尹治","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"尹治，生於五代梨園世家。\n\n在拍完《霸王別姬》後，尹治陸續拍攝了一些電影和電視劇，後來報考了中國戲曲學院導演系。他在央視播出的電視劇《荀慧生》中扮演了梅蘭芳，並得到觀眾的認可。此外，他在李少紅導演的《雷雨》中，曾飾演過京劇名角小白春。","name":"尹治","primary":false}}]}},"person_4010200_translations":{"at":1774698744945,"data":{"id":4010200,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Brehna Bahar","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PS","iso_639_1":"ps","name":"پښتو","english_name":"Pushto","data":{"biography":"","name":"Brehna Bahar","primary":true}}]}},"person_130562_translations":{"at":1774698745938,"data":{"id":130562,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Andrew Lin Hoi (Chinese: 連凱) is a Hong Kong actor, born in Taiwan, graduated from the Fine Arts Department of the University of California, Changdi, and went to Hong Kong in 1996 to develop his skills. He has participated in many movies and TV dramas. Starting his acting career in 1997, Lin Hoi has acted in 30 films and 18 TV series. This versatile and handsome actor can play both hero and villain. Before coming to Hong Kong in 1996, he was a special effects costume and makeup artist in the United States, where he helped many local film workers including Tsui Hark.","name":"Andrew Lin Hoi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"连凯，1969年8月7日出生于台湾台北，毕业于美国加州州立大学长滩分校美术系。中国内地影视男演员。\n\n1997年开始他的演艺生涯。2004年在参演连续剧《天涯侠医》。2005年主演了由张小娴小说改编的电视剧《如果月亮有眼睛》。2007年，主演电视剧《牟氏庄园》。2008年，参演电视剧《春去春又回》。2010年，主演都市悬疑电视剧《无懈可击之美女如云》。2011年，参演电影《不再让你孤单》。2012年，参演电视剧《龙门镖局》。2013年，主演情感剧《遇见王沥川》。2014年，主演电影《特工艾米拉》、《前任告急》。2015年，出演电影《破风》、《悬战》、《真相禁区》、《大唐玄奘》。同年12月，主演惊悚悬疑电影《失心者》。2016年7月，拍摄爱情轻喜剧《遇见下一个你》。2017年3月，友情出演《漂洋过海来看你》。同年，参演网络剧《小妖的金色城堡》。2018年，主演电视剧《谈判官》，参演电视剧《十年三月三十日》，主演电影《我说的都是真的》、《乐狱》。同年7月，参演电影《大天蓬》。8月，参演电影《天下第一镖局》。同月，参演电影《逃离贝尔格莱德》。9月，参演环保题材网络剧《野象环生》。","name":"连凯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"連凱","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Liên Khải","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"連凱，1969 年 8 月 7 日出生於台灣台北，畢業於美國加州州立大學長灘分校美術系。中國內地影視男演員。","name":"連凱","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Andrew Lin Hoi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Л